        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You're adept at revealing—or creating—fear among those who threaten civilization. If you succeed at a check to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Recall Knowledge] to identify an animal, beast, fungus, or plant, you get a critical success instead. Additionally, whenever you critically succeed at a check to Recall Knowledge against an animal, beast, fungus, or plant, that creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 1}.</p>"
        },
